-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|												|
|This repository contains two versions of MD code (Especially for the Ar crystal simulation).	|
|												|
|(1) one original version of non-homogeneuos FCC Ar crstal.					|
|												|
|	The original version uses Verlet iterator to solve the Newton equations of motion.	|
|	PBC condition is applied.								|
|												|
|(2) one optimized version of non-homogeneuos FCC Ar crystal.					|
|												|
|	The optimized version pluses the neighbor-list method and is parallelized.		|
|												|
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|												|
|Compile the main/ module file with Intel/gcc compilor mpi version.	                	|
|							Designed & Edited: Shi-Lin WANG,2019 	|
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
